Requires: authconfig  
Requires: bind  
Requires: initscripts  
Requires: iptables  
Requires: module-init-tools  
Requires: nscd  
Requires: nss  
Requires: openssh-server  
Requires: radvd  
Requires: rpm  
Requires: selinux-policy
Requires: setup  
Requires: smartmontools  
Requires: sudo  
Requires: syslog 
Requires: xml-common  
